<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="H94079AA892E543AEA3A2500EF8BA85D6"><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">That the following named Members be, and are hereby, elected to the following standing committees of the House of Representatives:</text> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HAS00"> Committee on Armed Services:</committee-name> </header><text>Mr. Conaway.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HED00"> Committee on Education and Workforce:</committee-name> </header><text>Mrs. Grijalva.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HHM00"> Committee on Homeland Security:</committee-name> </header><text>Mr. Walkinshaw (to rank immediately after Ms. Pou).</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HII00"> Committee on Natural Resources:</committee-name> </header><text>Mrs. Grijalva (to rank immediately after Ms. Rivas).</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> </section> </resolution-body> <attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Kevin F. McCumber,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation> </resolution> 

